Writing Test Cases
High-level test cases are broad, contains no data
This was discussed in the ISTQB Foundation Level
High-level test cases are good if you have testers with experience
Copy of Testing Bootcamp 2024 Test Cases
No two test cases should have the same title
Two approaches:
Execute all the valid scenarios first with all their priorities and then go to invalid scenarios
Executing valid scenarios and some invalid scenarios depending on their priority level
Section 7 - Test Case Writing Task
Localization Testing refers to testing software with input data in a different language to ensure that it functions correctly and that language-specific elements are properly adapted
